{"type":"text","timestamp":1783487383524,"sessionID":"ses_0bfdf923effeJgm1s2MxRoJ0VL","part":{"id":"prt_f4021b9f3001Gin75ZJ4tMC17M","messageID":"msg_f402178d2001lCxl43ZiM71ti4","sessionID":"ses_0bfdf923effeJgm1s2MxRoJ0VL","type":"text","text":"The stock reducer command takes only the spec folder in the YAML, so I need to verify whether it honors the fan-out artifact override before running anything that could write outside the lineage boundary.","time":{"start":1783487379955,"end":1783487383522},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_07dd67b12aed8e19016a4ddb93f5f881919781905dbb32e0f4","phase":"commentary"}}}}
