{"type":"text","timestamp":1783487421058,"sessionID":"ses_0bfdf923effeJgm1s2MxRoJ0VL","part":{"id":"prt_f40224483001Ooypb4W9g67UjH","messageID":"msg_f4021ec5d001sh0aUR2w63ALiC","sessionID":"ses_0bfdf923effeJgm1s2MxRoJ0VL","type":"text","text":"The reducer currently resolves from `spec_folder` and does not accept the lineage override, so running it as-is would violate the requested write boundary. I’ll generate the reducer-shaped registry/dashboard/resource-map inside the lineage directory directly, and use the mechanical verifier with `--artifact-dir` for packet validation.","time":{"start":1783487415427,"end":1783487421056},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_03cbdc9f30d7e267016a4ddbb75f4881938b54d2eebd31b788","phase":"commentary"}}}}
