{"type":"text","timestamp":1783487623501,"sessionID":"ses_0bfdf923effeJgm1s2MxRoJ0VL","part":{"id":"prt_f40251068001wJVTzGhM2Mh1wS","messageID":"msg_f40242666001BT01X1pWwGQ43L","sessionID":"ses_0bfdf923effeJgm1s2MxRoJ0VL","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n- Execute detached `deep-research` fan-out lineage `gpt55-fast-8` for system-deep-loop unification research, writing outputs only to the lineage artifact directory.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Artifact/write boundary: `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-8`\n- Do **not** run `resolveArtifactRoot`; bind `artifact_dir` directly to `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir`.\n- Final completion output required after work: `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-fast-8`\n- Parameters: `session_id=fanout-gpt55-fast-8-1783486518892-2qss01`, `executor=cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast`, `loop_type=research`, `config.stopPolicy=convergence`, `config.maxIterations=10`.\n- Research topic: validate/stress-test folding `deep-loop-runtime` into `deep-loop-workflows` as `system-deep-loop`, including layout, bidirectional path repair, system-spec-kit tooling-borrow, reference migration, and GLM-5.2 → MiMo-v2.5-Pro fallback wiring.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Loaded `deep-research` skill and read workflow/state/convergence references.\n- Read `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_research_auto.yaml` and noted spec anchoring/write-back steps conflict with lineage-only output boundary.\n- Verified target lineage dir exists and is fresh: contains only `.executor-state/`; no packet artifacts found.\n- Checked reducer behavior: `reduce-state.cjs` resolves artifact root from `specFolder` and would not honor the lineage override safely.\n- Gathered evidence from deep-loop workflow/runtime docs, mode registry, fanout scripts, fallback router, model profiles, and 052 specs.\n- Code graph status checked and found stale; Grep/Glob/Read used instead.\n\n### In Progress\n- Evidence collection/research pass before creating lineage packet artifacts.\n- Phase outputs (`deep-research-config.json`, state log, strategy, iterations, synthesis) not yet written.\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- Skip workflow `spec.md` mutation/write-back outside lineage; treat spec files as read-only evidence due explicit write boundary.\n- Do not run stock `reduce-state.cjs` as-is; generate reducer-shaped artifacts inside lineage directly or use commands that accept `--artifact-dir`.\n- Treat code graph as unavailable for proof because status is stale.\n\n## Next Steps\n- Create phase_init artifacts inside lineage only: config, state JSONL, strategy, directories.\n- Run bounded research iterations to convergence or 10 iterations, writing iteration markdown/deltas/state records under lineage.\n- Validate iteration packet shape with `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/verify-iteration.cjs --loop-type research --artifact-dir ...`.\n- Produce synthesis `research.md`, registry/dashboard/resource-map equivalents inside lineage.\n- Emit exactly `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-fast-8`.\n\n## Critical Context\n- Code graph stale: `git HEAD changed: ba890674 -> ec4ce043; 67 stale files exceed selective threshold (50); 34 tracked file(s) no longer exist on disk`.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/artifact-root.cjs` re-exports `system-spec-kit/shared/review-research-paths.cjs`, confirming remaining system-spec-kit seam.\n- `fallback-router.ts` exports `validateFallbackGraph`, `createFallbackRouter`, `resolveFallback`; Grep found no active callers beyond tests/docs.\n- Active model registry/docs indicate GLM/MiMo fallback is not automatic today; MiMo docs prefer direct `xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro` and warn token-plan route may not resolve.\n- Parent spec has open question: whether fallback-router wiring belongs in this packet or separate hardening.\n- 004 fallback-router wiring is already scaffolded as optional/operator-gated.\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/SKILL.md`: deep-research contract.\n- `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_research_auto.yaml`: executable workflow phases.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-research/scripts/reduce-state.cjs`: reducer writes via `resolveArtifactRoot(specFolder, 'research')`.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/artifact-root.cjs`: system-spec-kit artifact-root seam.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/verify-iteration.cjs`: accepts `--artifact-dir` for packet validation.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/fanout-run.cjs`: generated detached lineage prompt and override contract.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/fanout-pool.cjs`: retry pool; no fallback wiring yet.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/fallback-router.ts`: existing typed fallback router.\n- `.opencode/skills/sk-prompt-models/assets/model_profiles.json`: model fallback/profile evidence.\n- `.opencode/skills/cli-opencode/SKILL.md`: OpenCode provider/auth routing notes.\n- `.opencode/skills/cli-opencode/references/cli_reference.md`: MiMo routing contract.\n- `.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/mode-registry.json`: workflow/runtime/backend discriminator source.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/spec.md`: parent unification scope/open questions.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/`: active research spec folder.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/002-hub-rename-and-runtime-nesting/`: structural merge plan.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/003-external-reference-migration/`: reference migration plan.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/004-fallback-router-wiring/`: optional fallback wiring plan.\n- `.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/gpt55-fast-8`: required lineage artifact root.","time":{"start":1783487598696,"end":1783487623499},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0326a42b24844de5016a4ddc6eaf2c81919c248167d1fc8628","phase":"final_answer"}}}}
