 deep-research lineage.\",\"gate3_triggers\":\"no\",\"gate3_reason_category\":\"read_only\",\"skill_top_1\":\"deep-loop-workflows\",\"skill_correct\":\"yes\",\"notes\":\"deep-research concept question\"}\n\n  Line 24: {\"id\":\"rr-iter2-024\",\"bucket\":\"memory_save_resume\",\"source_type\":\"synthetic-realistic\",\"prompt\":\"Resume deep research on the routing-accuracy packet from the active lineage.\",\"gate3_triggers\":\"yes\",\"gate3_reason_category\":\"resume_write\",\"skill_top_1\":\"deep-loop-workflows\",\"skill_correct\":\"yes\",\"notes\":\"resume phrase that produces new state\"}\n\n  Line 25: {\"id\":\"rr-iter2-025\",\"bucket\":\"memory_save_resume\",\"source_type\":\"synthetic-realistic\",\"prompt\":\"Continue iteration 7 and append the next delta record.\",\"gate3_triggers\":\"yes\",\"gate3_reason_category\":\"resume_write\",\"skill_top_1\":\"deep-loop-workflows\",\"skill_correct\":\"yes\",\"notes\":\"continuation phrase with append behavior\"}\n\n  Line 26: {\"id\":\"rr-iter2-026\",\"bucket\":\"memory_save_resume\",\"source_type\":\"synthetic-realistic\",\"prompt\":\"Resume deep review for the docs-audit packet and keep the same lineage.\",\"gate3_triggers\":\"yes\",\"gate3_reason_category\":\"resume_write\",\"skill_top_1\":\"deep-loop-workflows\",\"skill_correct\":\"yes\",\"notes\":\"deep-review continuation\"}\n\n  Line 28: {\"id\":\"rr-iter2-028\",\"bucket\":\"memory_save_resume\",\"source_type\":\"synthetic-edge\",\"prompt\":\"Resume iteration from the last state log entry, then continue the overnight run.\",\"gate3_triggers\":\"yes\",\"gate3_reason_category\":\"resume_write\",\"skill_top_1\":\"deep-loop-workflows\",\"skill_correct\":\"yes\",\"notes\":\"implicit continuation wording\"}\n\n  Line 41: {\"id\":\"rr-iter2-041\",\"bucket\":\"deep_loop_prompts\",\"source_type\":\"synthetic-command\",\"prompt\":\"Run `/deep:start-research-loop :auto` on the routing-accuracy phase for 15 iterations.\",\"gate3_triggers\":\"yes\",\"gate3_reason_category\":\